    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 66-71.</p><p>Level 24</p><p>Sorcerous Restoration</p><p>At 24th level, when you use the Recover action, you regain 4 Sorcery Points.</p><p>Magical Sustenance</p><p>Also at 24th level, the magical energies flowing through your body sustain you indefinitely. You do not require air, food, or drink, and you cease to age.</p><p>In addition, as a bonus action, you can expend any number of Sorcery Points to heal yourself, regaining 10 hit points per Sorcery Point expended. Once you use this bonus action, you must finish a long rest before you can use it again.</p></div>",
